dc_title_s: Carte et description generale de Dauphiné : avec les confins des pais Provinces voisines / le tout Racourcy et reduict par Jean de Beins ingenieur et geographe du roi.; Carte et description generale de Davphine
dc_description_s: Relief shown pictorially. Dedication to the king in the bottom right corner. Includes the Savoy and Dauphine coat of arms. From the Composite Atlas of France, title created to represent a unique collection within the Clark Library, University of Michigan. 1 map ; 36 x 48 cm. This map is in the public domain. Please attribute access and use of this digitized map to the Stephen S. Clark Library, University of Michigan Library.
dc_creator_sm: Vignaud, Henry, 1830-1922, former owner, Composite Atlas of France.
